<b>"RE: Why Everquest and not AC/Darktide?"</b><br>
Posted by Kyriel  on 12-07-01 at 02:30&nbsp;PM<br>
<blockquote>
NPC manipulation and turn based combat are not the be-all end-all of PvP.  In my opinion, a more twitch based scheme is preferable to pure turn based, even timed turn based.  Of course, if you think otherwise, that is a pretty good reason for not being in AC.<P>And yeah.. you do need to keep exping now and then, both to burn vitae and to edge closer to the exp-chain whored characters.  You could of course build your own chain, but that would require somebody to keep leveling.. and KAAOS doesn't have a history of inviting in loads of carebears to provide them with exp.<P>Logical, at least.
</blockquote>
